      {
        "text": "Performance:Amazing performance\n\nFirst off, it's a very handsome and beefy card. Ignore the odd pcie cable 😅.\nFinishing wise it looks mostly good.\nIt's an exceptionally strong card, price wise and sheer horsepower. It does so well on 1440P, Ultra. Depending on the game you can easily get 180-200 fps, native and some with framegen. Pragmata (demo), Stellar Blade runs like a dream (MH Wilds still runs poorly)\nFSR4 is a huge improvement over FSR 3.1.\n\nThe fans however are jet loud out of the box especially on performance mode, requiring a custom fan curve to have acceptable noise.\n\nI don't hear any coil whine from the card.\n750w PSU is fine but you might need to change to a better PSU (850w gold) to avoid buzzing noise leaking into studio monitors like mine.\n\nIt's a great card overall. Thanks so much ALL It.\nDefinitely my go to place for GPUs, they're very good.",
